contributionDescription:
contribution for Smerdyakov from OpenX team. Trough his thinking the OpenX team delivered cool OP native products. OpenX is a small team committed to Optimism, making public decentralized goods there. top products;

- (ve)NFT market; dedicated interface for veNFT trading moving traffic from OpenSea to OpenX (OP Native) Unique innovations: 1) trade in any NFT for any ERC token, 2) displaying discount %'s of veNFT vs market rate, 3) only 1% trading fee, only to cover bare cost

- opxvelo is now a decentralized liquid wrapper of vevelo where the voting power is committed to those who LP with it (1opxvelo in LP = 1 vevelo vote). This makes it effective a decentralized liquid wrapper, and allows ecosystem projects to get a certain baseline of APR without bribing and regardless of TVL in LP.
